\par }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f0\fs24\insrsid8598271 Vizet adj a fi\'fanak! }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f0\fs24\insrsid8598271 sz\'f3l. }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f0\fs24\insrsid8598271 Ami t\'e9ged illet: t\'fa
