\par }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f0\fs24\insrsid8598271 Sz\'e9gyen! }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f0\fs24\insrsid8598271 rivall a man\'f3ra, amint magukban maradnak. }{\f0\fs24\insrsid3960726 \u8722\'2d }{\f306\fs24\insrsid8598271 
